snippet.title: Broke Alchemist Emma's Debt Repayment Plan - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Emma, a young alchemist living in Echichi Town, suddenly has to repay a debt of 1,000,000 gold after her mother, Beth, goes missing. As it turns out, Beth had a debt with the Baron, but was unable to repay it due to unknown circumstances. Will Emma be able to repay this immense amount of money?
